      <title>建国 250 周年政治紧张局势加剧，民主党与特朗普发生冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/04/us/politics/democrats-clash-trump-america-250th-birthday.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2028 年大选的潜在竞争者加文·纽瑟姆 (Gavin Newsom) 和韦斯·摩尔 (Wes Moore) 将特朗普总统的记录视为对美国理想的背叛，而总统则贬低他们的政党极端。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/04/us/politics/democrats-clash-trump-america-250th-birthday.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 Jul 2026 21:04:59 GMT</pubDate>
