    <item>
      <title>阿利托法官没有表示他准备辞去最高法院职务</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/04/us/politics/justice-alito-influence-supreme-court.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本任期内，阿利托大法官在投票权、移民和枪支问题上为保守派带来了重大胜利。他没有表示他已准备好辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/04/us/politics/justice-alito-influence-supreme-court.html</guid>
